Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,a,,0,0,0,,（じゃりまん狩り—Japari Bun Harvesting）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:17.74,a,margay,0,0,0,,集まってもらってすみません！\NSorry for making you guys come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:19.49,a,princess,0,0,0,,どうしたの、マーゲイ？\NWhat's the matter, Margay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.39,a,princess,0,0,0,,今日はオフの日だって。\NI thought today was an off day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:23.64,a,gen,0,0,0,,何かあれば、お手伝いしますよ。\NWe'll help you out if you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.55,a,margay,0,0,0,,えーっとですね…\NWell, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:30.00,a,margay,0,0,0,,ハカセ達から頼まれまして、一つお仕事をお願いしたいんです。\NI'd like to ask your assistance in a favor from the owls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:34.28,a,koutei,0,0,0,,直々にとは珍しいな。どんな仕事なんだ？\NIt's rare for them to be so personal. What kind of favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:36.10,a,margay,0,0,0,,ジャパリまんを百個！\NWe need to provide 100 Japari buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.48,0:00:40.35,a,margay,0,0,0,,できれば、二百個以上用意して欲しいとのことです。\NMore than 200, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.98,a,hululu,0,0,0,,ジャパリまん～\NJapari buns~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:44.83,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,フルル、食べてんじゃねぇよ…\NHululu, we're not eating..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.27,a,gen,0,0,0,,あ、かばんさんが今度、旅に出るから？\NAh, is this for Kaban-san's journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:52.49,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ん？それって、ボスが用意させたんじゃなかったか？\NHuh? Didn't Boss prepare that for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:55.93,a,princess,0,0,0,,あれよ、コウテイ！サーバルが付いて行くでしょう？\NIsn't Serval following along? That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.92,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ああ、なるほど。\NAh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:03.56,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,あいつ、自分で食べ物取れずに、飢え死にしそうだもんな…\NNot bringing along her own food... she'll die of starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.60,a,margay,0,0,0,,大体この袋いっぱいで、二百個らしいです！\NWe need to prepare 200 buns, just about enough to fill this sack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.27,a,margay,0,0,0,,お願いできますか？\NCan you girls do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.29,a,gen,0,0,0,,分かりました！\NGot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:13.15,a,princess,0,0,0,,百個…結構な量よね…\N100 buns... that's quite the amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:16.02,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ボスは食べる分しかくれねぇしなぁ…\NBut Boss only gives us as much as we need to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:18.52,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,精々五、六個だよな？\NAbout 5, 6 buns at the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:21.14,a,koutei,0,0,0,,何か当てがあればいいのだが…\NIf only there was something we could rely on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:24.67,a,princess,0,0,0,,プリンセス、島にそういう所ってないか？\NPrincess, is there a place for that somewhere in this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:30.79,a,princess,0,0,0,,噂で、ボスがジャパリまんを作っている場所があるって、聞いたことあるけど…\NWell, I heard rumors that there is a place where Boss makes Japari Buns...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:36.51,a,gen,0,0,0,,ああ、私も聞いたことあります、でも誰も見たことないんですよね。\NAh! I've also heard that. But no one's ever actually seen it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:38.11,a,margay,0,0,0,,まさにハカセが、\NIt must be that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:41.46,a,margay,0,0,0,,「そこに行ってちょいちょいしてくるのです」、と！\Nthe professor wants us to "go real quick and do it for us".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:42.75,a,princess,0,0,0,,ええ？\NEhh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:48.30,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,まあ、この先食べる分には変わりないから、前以て貰う感じか。\NWell, it's not like the amount they're eating will change in the future. It'll be like getting it in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:50.68,a,koutei,0,0,0,,それって、どこにあるんだ？\NWell, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:51.86,a,margay,0,0,0,,それが、\NWell, they said,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:56.60,a,margay,0,0,0,,「では頼んだですよ。我々忙しいのです。」\N"We're leaving the rest to you. We are busy."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:00.35,a,margay,0,0,0,,「ハカセ。行きましょう。じゅるり。」\N"Let us go, professor. Slurp."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:05.40,a,margay,0,0,0,,「行きますか、ジョシュ。じゅるり。」、と。\N"Let us go, assistant. Slurp."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:06.94,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,丸投げかよ！\NThey're dumping it all on us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:10.01,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,あの二人、本当に忙しいのか？\NAre those two actually busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:13.90,a,princess,0,0,0,,うぅぅ…他のフレンズに聞いてみましょうか！\NHrmm... Let's go ask other Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.54,a,koutei,0,0,0,,サーバル達のためだ。頑張ろう！\NIt's for Serval and Kaban. Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:24.40,a,princess,0,0,0,,何人か聞いてみたけど、誰も知らないわね。\NWe asked a bunch of Friends, but none of them knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:28.94,a,koutei,0,0,0,,みんな自分の縄張りの外は、そこまで詳しくないからなぁ。\NWell, they wouldn't know about much outside of their territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.84,a,serval,0,0,0,,あれ？PPPのみんな、どうしたの？\NHm? Hey, PPP, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:36.76,a,kaban,0,0,0,,こんにちは！この前はありがとうございました。\NHello! Thanks for your help last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.47,a,gen,0,0,0,,いえいえかばんさん、こちらこそ！\NNot at all, Kaban-san. We owe it to you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:41.55,a,,0,0,0,,お元気そうで何よりです。\NWe're glad that you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:44.97,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,よう、サーバル。今ジャパリまんを探しててな！\NYo, Serval! We're looking for Japari buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.32,a,serval,0,0,0,,へぇ、なんでなんで？何かやるの？\NHuh! Why; what are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:52.66,a,hululu,0,0,0,,それはね、サーバルがかばんちゃんに付いて行く時に…\NIt's for when you're going to follow Kaban...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.11,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ちょ、ちょ、ちょっと事情があってさ…\NW-Well, we have our reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.60,a,princess,0,0,0,,それで、ジャパリまんを作ってる所を探してるの！\NAnd so we're looking for where Japari buns are made!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:03.86,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ボスが作ってる所があるらしいんだけど、誰も知らないんだ。\NSupposedly there's a place where Boss makes them, but no one knows where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:07.61,a,serval,0,0,0,,そうなんだ。あたしも知らないな。\NI see. I don't know either...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.60,a,serval,0,0,0,,かばんちゃん、何かいい案ないかな？\NKaban-chan, do you have any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:17.09,a,kaban,0,0,0,,そうだ！ジャパリまんを配ってるラッキーさん、\NI know! When Lucky-san has no more Japari buns to distribute,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:20.95,a,kaban,0,0,0,,籠が空になったら新しいのを取りに行くだろうから、\Nit'll go back to fetch some more;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:24.11,a,kaban,0,0,0,,それに付いて行ってみる！ってどうでしょう。\NLet's try to follow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:26.26,a,gen,0,0,0,,なるほど！\NI see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.27,a,koutei,0,0,0,,かばんはさすがだな！\NYou're amazing as usual, Kaban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:29.85,a,princess,0,0,0,,早速探すわよ！\NLet's go find one now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.88,a,ppp,0,0,0,,おぅー！\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:43.36,a,kaban,0,0,0,,よく分からないけど、力になれたｘよかった。\NI don't really get it, but I'm glad I was able to help out.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,a,,0,0,0,,力になれたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.82,a,serval,0,0,0,,私達も遊びに行こう！\NLet's also go and have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:50.33,a,serval,0,0,0,,あ、アリツカゲラが寝床の見つけ方を教えてくれるって言ってたよ！\NOh yeah, Campo Flick said she would teach us how to find a place to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.63,a,serval,0,0,0,,行ってみない？\NWanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:52.36,a,kaban,0,0,0,,うん！\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.65,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ボス、ボス…\NBoss... Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:05.56,a,koutei,0,0,0,,籠を持ったボス…\NA Boss with a basket...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:10.12,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,いつもジャパリまんがなくなった頃にふらっと現れるんだよなぁ。\NHe always appears out of nowhere when we're out of Japari buns...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.12,a,princess,0,0,0,,いたわよ！\NThere it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.08,a,gen,0,0,0,,ちょうどフレンズが貰いに来てますね。\NIt seems like a bunch of Friends have just come to get them.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,a,,0,0,0,,pastebin translation + komica has 群れに, but this doesn't seem quite right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.77,a,koutei,0,0,0,,残り、あと二、三個ぐらいか。\NThere's about 2 or 3 buns left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:22.27,a,hululu,0,0,0,,いいなぁ、あたしも食べたいなぁ…\NAww, I want some too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.00,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,お前、さっき喰ってなかったか？\NDidn't you already eat just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:27.15,a,gen,0,0,0,,ああ！なくなりましたよ！\NAh! There's no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.80,a,princess,0,0,0,,どうするのかしら…\NWhat shall we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:33.00,a,koutei,0,0,0,,考えた事がなかったなぁ。\NWe didn't think about that, did we...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.03,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,歩き始めたぜ。\NHe's started to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.45,a,princess,0,0,0,,追いかけましょう！\NLet's follow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:52.01,a,koutei,0,0,0,,うう…この体とは言え、\NUrgh... it's actually pretty hard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:56.03,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ぼこぼこした所を歩くのは、苦手だ…\Nto walk on rough paths in this body...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.58,a,hululu,0,0,0,,そう？\NIs that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.71,a,princess,0,0,0,,無理しちゃダメよ、コウテイ\NDon't push yourself too hard, Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.11,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ボスを見失わないようにしないとな！\NWe can't lose sight of Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.74,a,gen,0,0,0,,あ！何か見えてきましたよ。\NAh! I see something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.89,a,princess,0,0,0,,崖に穴が…\NThere's a hole in the cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:09.63,a,princess,0,0,0,,トンネルかしら?\NIs it a tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:13.45,a,gen,0,0,0,,入口の左右に、別のボスがいますね。\NThere are other Bosses around the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:16.41,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,籠持ったボスが、中に入ってくぞ！\NA Boss with a basket is entering!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:17.55,a,princess,0,0,0,,追いかけましょう！\NLet's follow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.48,a,princess,0,0,0,,な、何？なんで邪魔するの？\NH-huh? Why are you obstructing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.60,a,gen,0,0,0,,ボス、怒ってますね。\NIt looks like Boss is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.77,a,princess,0,0,0,,ちょ、ちょっと離れるわよ。\NI-I'll move farther away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.60,a,koutei,0,0,0,,どうしようか。\NWhat do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.31,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ちょっと、無理して間を取ってみるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:44.03,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,でもよ、ボスを怒らせると、追いかける所じゃなくなるぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:48.52,a,gen,0,0,0,,ボスとお話できるかばんさんに、説得をお願いしてみますか？\NKaban-san can talk to Bosses. Should we try and ask her to persuade Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:52.83,a,princess,0,0,0,,でも、サーバルが付いて行くことはまだ内緒にしてあげなくちゃ…\NBut then, we have to keep secret the fact that Serval is tagging along...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.88,a,princess,0,0,0,,あまり話したらバレちゃうわよ。\NIf we say too much, she'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:05:58.53,a,giant,0,0,0,,よ！\NYo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:05:59.53,a,ppp,0,0,0,,うわぁ！\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:00.84,a,giant,0,0,0,,かさ…こそ。\NRustle...rustle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.23,a,giant,0,0,0,,かさ、こそ、かさ…\NRustle, rustle, rustle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:02.79,a,ppp,0,0,0,,へぇ？\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.16,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ジャイアント先輩！？\NGiant-senpai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:07.78,a,giant,0,0,0,,何だ？まだ見つかってないのか？ジャパリまん。\NWhat? Haven't you girls found any Japari buns yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.44,a,hululu,0,0,0,,そうなの…\NNo, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.37,a,princess,0,0,0,,っていうか、なんでそれを知ってるんですか？\NBut how on earth did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:15.30,a,koutei,0,0,0,,相変わらず、謎の多い…\NMysterious, as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.99,a,giant,0,0,0,,しっしっしっし。\NHehehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.97,a,gen,0,0,0,,それが、あそこの入口からボスが入れてくれなくて…\NWell, the Bosses won't let us in through the entrance over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:22.36,a,giant,0,0,0,,なるほどな。\NI seel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:28.13,a,giant,0,0,0,,じゃあ、ラッキービーストの前で心底困ってるふりをしてみろ。\NHow about pretending to be sincerely troubled in front of Lucky Beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.47,a,princess,0,0,0,,困ってるふり？\NPretending to be troubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.71,a,giant,0,0,0,,あいつは人しか助けないわけじゃない。\NIt's not that that thing helps people only.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:37.66,a,giant,0,0,0,,なんだかんだ困ってるフレンズがいると、サポートするんだ。\NBoss'll support Friends who are troubled about this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.24,a,hululu,0,0,0,,へぇー。\NHuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.66,a,giant,0,0,0,,じゃあな。\NSee ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:45.78,a,giant,0,0,0,,まあ、うまくやりなー。がさごそがさごそ。\NWell, try to do well. Rustle, rustle, rustle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.61,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,何だったんだ？\NWhat was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.62,a,koutei,0,0,0,,あの先輩の言う事は、なんだかんだ当たるｘ。
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,a,,0,0,0,,当たるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:53.89,a,princess,0,0,0,,やってみましょう！\NLet's try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.22,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,よう、ボス！\NYo, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.61,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,さらにロックなｘをするために、
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,a,,0,0,0,,生き方　/iɕ.kata/?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.56,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,そこを通してほしいんだ！\NI want to enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.20,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,えっ。\NUh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.43,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ロックってのはその…\NBy "rock" I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:09.71,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ほら、岸壁、とかさぁ、\NYou know, like cliffs, things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.71,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,困難を…\NOr rather, only by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.99,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,越えてこそ、っていうか…\Nconquering hardships... or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:19.96,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ダメだ。\NIt's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.26,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ボス怖ぇよ…\NBoss is too scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.03,a,hululu,0,0,0,,よしよしー。\NThere, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.72,a,koutei,0,0,0,,次は、私が行こう。\NI'll go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.86,a,koutei,0,0,0,,えっとだな、ボス。\NWell, um, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.22,a,koutei,0,0,0,,困ってるんだ。\NI need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.80,a,koutei,0,0,0,,私は、その。\NI, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.46,a,princess,0,0,0,,気絶してるー！\NShe's passed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:40.97,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ダメだ。\NIt's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.97,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ブリザードのような目だ。\NHer eyes are like a blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.90,a,hululu,0,0,0,,よしよしー。\NThere, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:46.70,a,princess,0,0,0,,ジェーン？\NGen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:52.47,a,gen,0,0,0,,ボス、私達、助けたい子がいて、\NBoss, there's a girl we want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.56,a,gen,0,0,0,,そのためにジャパリまんが必要なんです。\NIn order to do that, we need Japari buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:59.06,a,gen,0,0,0,,どうかそこ、通してもらえませんか？\NPlease, could you let us through?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:04.67,a,gen,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます！\NThank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.08,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,えぇ！？\NHuh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.94,a,hululu,0,0,0,,ジェーン、すごーい！\NGen, you're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.56,a,princess,0,0,0,,さっすがね、ジェーン！\NNice one, Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.20,a,koutei,0,0,0,,正直が一番、と言う事か。\NI guess "honesty is the best policy", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.44,a,princess,0,0,0,,出口から光が射してるけど、\NThere's light coming from the exit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.26,a,princess,0,0,0,,薄暗いわね。\Nbut it's still pretty dark, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:26.85,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,いっ、てっ…\NOw...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:30.32,a,gen,0,0,0,,イワビーさん、跳ねたら頭をぶつけますよ。\NYou'll hit your head if you jump in here, Iwabi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.05,a,gen,0,0,0,,ゆっくり歩きましょう。\NLet's walk slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:37.80,a,koutei,0,0,0,,見えてきたわ。\NI can see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:43.72,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,うわぁー。\NWow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:46.04,a,gen,0,0,0,,大きい池ですね。\NWhat a huge lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.75,a,princess,0,0,0,,パークにこんな所があったなんて…\NFor a place like this to exist in the park...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.30,a,hululu,0,0,0,,島があるね。\NThere's an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.20,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ボスは、あそこだろうか。\NMaybe that's where Boss is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.25,a,koutei,0,0,0,,行こう。\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.32,a,koutei,0,0,0,,不思議な所だな。\NWhat a mysterious place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.70,a,gen,0,0,0,,木漏れ日が気持ちいいですね。\NThe sunlight through the trees feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.18,a,princess,0,0,0,,あ！見て！\NAh! Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.21,a,princess,0,0,0,,木にジャパリまんがぶら下がってる！\NJapari buns are hanging from the trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:25.76,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,しかも、すげぇ沢山あるぞ。\NAnd there's a lot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.40,a,koutei,0,0,0,,どう言う事だ？\NWhat could it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.54,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ジャパリまんって、木に生るのか？\NDo Japari buns grow on trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.68,a,gen,0,0,0,,あ！ボスですよ！\NAh! Bosses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:43.07,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ジャパリまんの束を投げて、木に引っ掛けてるぜ。\NThey're throwing bunches of Japari buns into the trees and letting them hang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.31,a,princess,0,0,0,,なにしてるのかしら。\NWhat are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:47.66,a,hululu,0,0,0,,キラキラして綺麗ー。\NIt's shiny and pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.42,a,gen,0,0,0,,行っちゃいましたね。\NThey left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.85,a,koutei,0,0,0,,あれは、どこから持ってきたんだろうか。\NWhere did they bring it here from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.24,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,チャンスだぜ。\NNow's our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.62,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ここにあるやつを、貰って行こう！\NLet's go get the ones here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.85,a,princess,0,0,0,,そうね。行きましょう！\NYou're right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.13,a,koutei,0,0,0,,これは…\NThis is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.89,a,koutei,0,0,0,,なかなか大変だな。\Nquite a tough job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:23.37,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,こういう細かい作業、未だに苦手なんだよなぁ。\NI'm still not good at such precise work yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:27.96,a,princess,0,0,0,,あの子達のために、少しでも多めに用意してあげないと…\NWe have to prepare a decent amount for those girls, if even a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.97,a,princess,0,0,0,,島の外に、食べ物があるか分からないもの！\NWe don't know if there's anything to eat outside of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:34.67,a,gen,0,0,0,,早くしないと、またボスが来そうですね。\NIf we don't hurry up, Boss will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:38.28,a,hululu,0,0,0,,よ、よ、よ、よ、よ、よ、よ、よ…\NHeave-ho, heave-ho- heave-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.36,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,すげぇ速いなぁ！\NMan, she's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:44.22,a,koutei,0,0,0,,フルル、ジャパリまんの事になると動きが…\NWhen it comes to Japari buns, Hululu'll work faster...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:48.40,a,gen,0,0,0,,すごいですね。一人で百個ぐらい集めてるんじゃないですか。\NAmazing. She's collected about 100 all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.61,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ああ！ボスが！\NAh! Bosses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.48,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ヤバい、見つかった！\NShoot, they've spotted us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.12,a,princess,0,0,0,,に、逃げましょう！\NL-let's make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:06.27,a,gen,0,0,0,,どうしましょう？どんどん増えてきてますよ！\NWhat do we do? More of them are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.33,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ひぃー！すごい怒ってるぜ！\NEek! They're really furious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.21,a,koutei,0,0,0,,泳いで逃げよう！池に飛び込むぞ！\NLet's get away by swimming. Jump into the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.74,a,princess,0,0,0,,えぇーい！\NAlley oop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:25.51,a,gen,0,0,0,,やっぱり水の中は落ち着くわね。\NIn the end, the water is pretty soothing, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.68,a,koutei,0,0,0,,よし。距離を稼ごう。\NAlright. Let's gather distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:28.67,a,gen,0,0,0,,ふん！\NMm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:31.76,a,hululu,0,0,0,,ジェーン相変わらず速ーい。\NGen is fast as always~.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.17,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,行くぜ行くぜ！\NLet's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.13,a,hululu,0,0,0,,イワビー相変わらず速ーい。\NIwabi is fast as always~.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.82,a,koutei,0,0,0,,よし。大分撒いたな。\NAlright. We've shaken them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.43,a,princess,0,0,0,,このまま一気に出口まで！\NLet's keep this pace all the way to the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.70,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,トンネルの中からもボスが！\NThere are more Bosses coming from the tunnel too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.32,a,koutei,0,0,0,,うっ、うぅえ…\NU, uurgh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:59.88,a,gen,0,0,0,,どうしよう？後ろからも沢山来ますよ。\NWhat do we do? There's a bunch of them coming from behind too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:02.46,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,ひぃー！ダメだ！\NEek! It's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.07,a,princess,0,0,0,,くっ…ここまでなの？\NDarn! Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.43,a,,0,0,0,,わっせ、わっせ、わっせ、わっせ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.06,a,araisan,0,0,0,,一番乗りなのだ！\NWe're the first to arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.10,a,boss,0,0,0,,うっ。\NOof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:14.22,a,koutei,0,0,0,,え？\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:15.28,a,princess,0,0,0,,何？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.62,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,なんだ、なんだ？\NWhat is it? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:19.00,a,araisan,0,0,0,,真ん丸はどこにあるのだ！\NWhere's the round thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.84,a,araisan,0,0,0,,どこなのだ！\NWhere is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:25.01,a,fennec,0,0,0,,あれー？今は何かにぶつかったようなー…\NHuh? It seems like we hit something just right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.84,a,,0,0,0,,あなた達は確か…\NYou guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.32,a,araisan,0,0,0,,アライさんなのだ！\NI'm Arai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.24,a,fennec,0,0,0,,フェネクスなのさー。\NI'm Fennec.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.36,a,hululu,0,0,0,,わぁ、何これ。\NWow, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:36.69,a,araisan,0,0,0,,ふっふーん。これは、「ばすてき」って言うのだ！\NHeheh. It's a "bus-ish"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.64,a,araisan,0,0,0,,ハカセに貰ったのだ！\NThe Professor gave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.00,a,koutei,0,0,0,,へぇ。\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.45,a,boss,0,0,0,,わ…わ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:45.64,a,fennec,0,0,0,,あ。アライさん、大変だよー。\NAh. Bad news, Arai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.15,a,fennec,0,0,0,,どうやらボスを撥ねちゃったみたいだねー。\NIt seems like we hit a Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:52.95,a,araisan,0,0,0,,え？あ！へぇ！？\NHuh? Ah! What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:58.06,a,araisan,0,0,0,,ご、ご、ごめんなさいなのだ、ボス！\NI-I-I'm sorry, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.88,a,fennec,0,0,0,,体は大丈夫みたいだねー。\NIt seems like their body is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:04.43,a,fennec,0,0,0,,でも、なんか怒ってるから逃げようかー。\NBut they seem kind of angry. Let's get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.93,a,araisan,0,0,0,,ひぃー！？\NEek!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:15.82,a,,0,0,0,,わっせ、わっせ、わっせ、わっせ、わっせ、わっせ、わっせ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.48,a,hululu,0,0,0,,速い、速ーい。\NWow, so fast~.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.36,a,princess,0,0,0,,助かったわ！\NYou saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.20,a,gen,0,0,0,,二人は、どうしてここに？\NSo, what are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.69,a,fennec,0,0,0,,こーんな格好の子がー、\NA girl who looked kind of like this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:28.11,a,fennec,0,0,0,,ここに私達の探し物があるって言ってたからー…\Nsaid that the thing we're looking for would be somewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:30.50,a,araisan,0,0,0,,真ん丸がなかったのだ！\NThere was no round thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.73,a,araisan,0,0,0,,騙されたのだ！\NShe tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.58,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ジャイアント先輩だ…\NIt must be Giant-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.07,a,princess,0,0,0,,全部お見通し、って事ね…\NShe saw it all coming, didn't she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:39.64,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,あの人怖ぇよ…\NMan, she's creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.92,a,gen,0,0,0,,取り敢えずよかった、ですかね。\NWell, we're okay for now, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.71,a,araisan,0,0,0,,よくないのだ！\NIt's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.79,a,araisan,0,0,0,,真ん丸がなかったのだ！\NThere's no round thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.24,a,fennec,0,0,0,,まあ、まあ。\NNow, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.89,a,fennec,0,0,0,,結果オーライでフレンズ助けになったっぽいよー。\NWe got out alright and helped out some Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.67,a,araisan,0,0,0,,オーラくないのだ！\NIt's not alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:55.62,a,araisan,0,0,0,,アライさんの今後の危機なのだ！\NArai-san's future is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.89,a,margay,0,0,0,,お、お疲れ様でしたー！\NThank you all so much for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.66,a,princess,0,0,0,,もー、めっちゃめっちゃ怖かったわよ！\NMan, it was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:10.74,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,いやー、歩いた泳いだ！\NAhh, we had a nice walk and a nice swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.61,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,いい汗かいたぜ！\NWorked up a good sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:18.69,a,araisan,0,0,0,,お前！真ん丸がないどころか、ボスに怒られたのだ！\NWhy you...! Now only was there not a round thing, but Boss got angry at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.35,a,araisan,0,0,0,,怖かったのだ！\NIt was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.21,a,giant,0,0,0,,まあ、まあ。ラッキービーストなんて、\NNow, now. In comparison to dinosaurs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:26.73,a,giant,0,0,0,,恐竜に比べたらかわいいもんだよ！\NLucky Beast is pretty cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.95,a,hululu,0,0,0,,キョーリュー？\NDyna-sore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.33,a,serval,0,0,0,,なんだか大変だったんだね！\NSounds like it was rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:33.23,a,serval,0,0,0,,料理食べる？もうすぐできるよ！\NWanna eat? It's almost ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.83,a,gen,0,0,0,,食べます、食べます。\NYes, yes, we'll eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.63,a,gen,0,0,0,,これが噂の、「料理」、ですか？\NIs this the "cooking" of legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:42.60,a,kaban,0,0,0,,今日は、ほとんどサーバルちゃんが作ってくれたんですよ。\NServal-chan cooked most of everything tiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:44.03,a,serval,0,0,0,,ふっふーん。\NThat's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:47.24,a,boss,0,0,0,,かばん。味見をちゃんとしてね。\NKaban. Make sure to taste-test it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:50.41,a,koutei,0,0,0,,いただこう。お腹がペコペコだよ。\NLet us eat. I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:53.43,a,serval,0,0,0,,ジャパリまん持ってないの？あげようか？\NDon't you guys have Japari buns? Should I give you some of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.72,a,koutei,0,0,0,,いや、持ってるんだが…\NNo, we have some, just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:58.03,a,koutei,0,0,0,,食べさしてやりたいやつがいてな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:14:59.60,a,koutei,0,0,0,,控えてるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.43,a,princess,0,0,0,,なんだか雛鳥みたいね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:06.42,a,hululu,0,0,0,,飲み込んで運べばよかったかもー。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:09.83,a,margay,0,0,0,,なっ！？それはいいですねー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.68,a,margay,0,0,0,,ペンギンさんらしい運搬方法！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:16.19,a,margay,0,0,0,,うへへ…一度ご馳走なりたいです…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.96,a,margay,0,0,0,,うへへ…はははは…へへへへ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.87,a,serval,0,0,0,,何の事か分からないけど、
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.35,a,serval,0,0,0,,私は普通に貰う方がいいかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:26.22,a,princess,0,0,0,,かばんは？今日どこに行ってたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:29.90,a,kaban,0,0,0,,今日は、アリツカゲラさんにお話を聞きに。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:32.10,a,kaban,0,0,0,,すごく勉強になりました！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:36.23,a,boss,0,0,0,,蟻塚に寝るのは、難しいかもしれないけど、
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:40.77,a,boss,0,0,0,,既にある物を寝床に利用するのは、大事な事だね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:41.42,a,koutei,0,0,0,,うわ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:42.65,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,へぇ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.67,a,princess,0,0,0,,すっかりボス恐怖症ね…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:49.14,a,hululu,0,0,0,,でもこのボスあまり怖くないね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:53.24,a,gen,0,0,0,,お話ができたら、他のボスも実は優しいのかも。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:56.80,a,koutei,0,0,0,,ところで、「まんまる」って、何なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:59.84,a,araisan,0,0,0,,ハカセに頼まれて、探しているのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.89,a,fennec,0,0,0,,サプライズでねー。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:04.17,a,fennec,0,0,0,,道のりは長いよー。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:07.87,a,iwabi,0,0,0,,こっちのこれも、サプライズだぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:12.62,a,serval,0,0,0,,そうなんだ！誰かを喜ばせるの？楽しみだね！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.08,a,kaban,0,0,0,,みんな、楽しそうですね！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.78,a,serval,0,0,0,,あ、料理ができたよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.32,a,serval,0,0,0,,食べよう、食べよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:24.94,a,giant,0,0,0,,料理か。久しぶりだなぁ。しっしっしっし。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.26,a,kaban,0,0,0,,ありがとう、サーバルちゃん。\NThank you, Serval-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:29.64,a,boss,0,0,0,,かばん、味見をちゃんとしてね。\NKaban. Make sure to taste-test it.
